<zk>
    <label multiline="true">
        1. Add these setting in zk.xml to enable WebSocket
        &lt;listener>
          &lt;listener-class>org.zkoss.zkmax.au.websocket.WebSocketWebAppInit&lt;/listener-class>
        &lt;/listener>
        &lt;library-property>
          &lt;name>org.zkoss.zkmax.au.websocket.WebSocketEndPoint.pingIntervalSecond&lt;/name>
          &lt;value>20&lt;/value>
        &lt;/library-property>
        2. Open the browser devtool to inspect the WebSocket "ping - pong" packets, currently only observable in Firefox and Safari.
    </label>
</zk>